---
title: Rich Chicken Thigh and Sweet Potato Curry with Buttery Basmati Rice
description: This quick and easy chicken curry recipe is full of flavour, with its rich, creamy tikka sauce and buttery basmati rice. Not only is this dish ready in no time, but it's also a dinner the whole family will love.
